getPrivateKey() - Method in class model.rsa.KeysGenerator
Method allows to get an instance of PrivateKey class previously generated in constructor, if constructor doesn't throw an exception, then method can't return null
getPrivateKey(String) - Method in class model.rsa.Algorithm
Method converts RSA Private Key from String to PublicKey format using PKCS #8 encoding and instance of KeyFactory class
getPublicKey() - Method in class model.rsa.KeysGenerator
Method allows to get an instance of PublicKey class previously generated in constructor, if constructor doesn't throw an exception, then method can't return null
getPublicKey(String) - Method in class model.rsa.Algorithm
Method converts RSA Public Key from String to PublicKey format using X.509 encoding and instance of KeyFactory class
